==English==
===Noun===
'''pulley'''
# One of the simple machines; a [[wheel]] with a [[groove]]d [[rim]] in which a pulled [[rope]] or [[chain]] will lift an object (more useful when two or more pulleys are used together such that a small force moving through a greater distance can exert a larger force through a smaller distance).

